      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I have babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly pristine shape\u2014not a scratch or a smudge to be found. I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel because it\u2019s a total dream. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
