    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend, maintained to a rigorous standard. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six features a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled, ensuring precise variable valve timing across the entire power band. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous transient response, pulling cleanly to the 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally pristine, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with a firm, positive shift action and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true, with all bushings and dampers providing the communicative feedback this platform is renowned for. Finished in Titanium Silver with a flawless Nappa leather interior, this is a turn-key, investment-grade machine with no deferred maintenance.",
